   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. The project at a glance\n",
    "\n",
    "PokeTeam AI takes a user's favourite Pokemon and recommends a six-member\n",
    "competitive team. It runs in two modes:\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Chaos mode** — the primary path. Uses real Smogon ladder usage data\n",
    "  (the *chaos JSON*) as a search heuristic and a trained LightGBM classifier\n",
    "  as a reranker. Returns teams that statistically resemble what real\n",
    "  high-rated players actually play.\n",
    "- **Synergy mode** — a graceful fallback. Pure rules (type effectiveness,\n",
    "  role balance, stat balance) for Pokemon that have no chaos data.\n",
    "\n",
    "The interesting work is in chaos mode, and that is what this notebook is\n",
    "mostly about. The architecture is *search plus rerank*: a beam search\n",
    "proposes candidate teams using teammate co-occurrence weights, and a small\n",
    "trained classifier reorders them. Neither piece does the whole job alone."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
