    "## 3. The data\n",
    "\n",
    "Three parquet tables sit at the heart of the project. They are produced from\n",
    "the raw Smogon chaos JSON by the parse stage of the pipeline. The schemas\n",
    "are:\n",
    "\n",
    "- `pokemon_meta` — one row per `(gen, tier, name)` with usage, viability,\n",
    "  base stats, types, role, weaknesses.\n",
    "- `teammates` — one row per `(gen, tier, a, b)` with the co-occurrence\n",
    "  weight between Pokemon `a` and `b`. This is the field the beam search\n",
    "  uses.\n",
    "- `movesets` — long format `(gen, tier, name, kind, value, weight)` for\n",
    "  moves, items, abilities, EV spreads, tera types, happiness. Used at\n",
    "  inference to enrich a recommended team."
   ]
  },
