    "## 4. The Teammates field — the heart of the project\n",
    "\n",
    "The Smogon `Teammates` field is the strongest signal in the whole pipeline.\n",
    "It records, for every pair of Pokemon, how often they co-occurred on the same\n",
    "team in real high-rated ladder games. This is observed human behaviour at\n",
    "scale, not a model's guess.\n",
    "\n",
    "To make this concrete, here are the top teammates for Salamence in Gen 3 OU.\n",
    "These are the names that the beam search will reach for first when asked\n",
