    "## 6. SVD embeddings — turning the teammate matrix into vectors\n",
    "\n",
    "The pipeline runs Singular Value Decomposition over the\n",
    "`(Pokemon × Pokemon)` teammate co-occurrence matrix to produce a 32-dimensional\n",
    "embedding per Pokemon. Pokemon with similar teammate profiles end up with\n",
    "similar embeddings, even if they never directly co-occurred.\n",
    "\n",
    "This is the same family of methods that powers Netflix-style collaborative\n",
    "filtering. The embeddings are not the recommendation themselves — they are\n",
    "features the LightGBM classifier consumes during training and inference."
   ]
  },
